en: Gachi is interacting with the furniture. Let's not disturb.
cnsimplified: Gachi正在与家具互动。让我们不要打扰。

en: " Gachi... I am about to leave to somewhere far. I hope these toys could keep you company as they did for me."
cnsimplified: “ Gachi ...我将要离开去个很远的地方。我希望这些玩具能陪伴你，像它们当初陪伴我一样。”

en: Things here have just been so hectic. I can’t believe it’s already the end of the year. I’m sorry that I have to tell you this, I won't be able to visit you for quite a while... busy. I am working on a project "Gachi-001",  here is my very first prototype
cnsimplified: 最近真的太忙了。我不敢相信已经是年底了。很抱歉，我不得不告诉您，我将很长时间无法拜访您。我正在研究“ Gachi-001”项目，这是我的第一个样板，希望能它能陪伴您。
